    <article itemscope="" data-type-id="1100" data-guid="1100-6532962">

            
            
    


        

  


        
        
              <section>

                  
          <div data-content-element-selector="p, .js-buylink-item-container" data-allowed-classes-selector="js-buylink-item-container">
                <p>Amazon has two <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0F2GYMC8H,B0DDJZW3C9&amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">great Meta Quest 3S VR headset bundles</a> in its <a href="https://www.gamespot.com/amazon-prime-day-deals/">Prime Big Deal Days sale</a>. The <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">128GB base model is available for only $249</a>, which matches the best-ever price for the best entry-level virtual reality headset around. As an added bonus, this is an Amazon-exclusive bundle with a bunch of free DLC for the popular online game Gorilla Tag. But if you love Batman, you may want to <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">opt for the 256GB model</a>, as it's on sale for a larger $71 discount and comes with the very cool Batman: Arkham Shadow VR game.</p><p>Amazon is also offering <a href="https://www.amazon.com/stores/page/preview?isSlp=1&amp;isPreview=1&amp;asins=B0F2GYMC8H,B0DDJZW3C9,B09MJRJ3C8,B09H68287R,B0CPYMDPB5,B0CD15C641,B081SHD773&amp;tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">discounts on Meta's official Quest 3S accessories</a>, including the <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Elite Strap</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Elite Strap with Battery</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Link Cable</a>, <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Compact Carrying Case</a>, and <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09MJRJ3C8?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Carrying Case</a> for headset with the Elite Strap. Take a look at all of the deals below before they expire on October 9 at 12 AM.</p><div title="6532962 - Prime Day Meta Quest 3S headset deals" data-embed-type="buylink" data-ref-id="3819" data-template="4" data-size="buylink__listicle" data-title="6532962 - Prime Day Meta Quest 3S headset deals" data-collection="">                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest 3S 128GB - Gorilla Tag Bundle</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0F2GYMC8H?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$249 (was $300) | Exclusive to Amazon</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>This Amazon-exclusive bundle comes with $45 worth of in-game content for Gorilla Tag, a popular free-to-play online game starring gorillas without legs who love playing variations of tag. The freebie is called the Cardboard Hero Bundle, and it includes 1,000 shiny rocks as well as the Handiwork Helmet and Armor. If you've never subscribed to Meta Horizon+, you'll also get three free months of the Game Pass-esque service. In addition to granting access to a rotating library of games, subscribers get two free games each month, and you get to keep them even if you cancel your subscription.</p><p>The Quest 3S is a lightweight, standalone VR headset that comes with two wireless Touch Plus controllers. It's strong enough to play a wide range of impressive VR games directly on the headset's internal hardware, including showpiece titles like Batman: Arkham Shadow, Asgard's Wrath 2, and Assassin's Creed Nexus. For VR games like Half Life: Alyx that are beyond its built-in capabilities, the Quest 3S can be synced to wirelessly to a gaming PC or with a compatible link cable. You can also cloud stream games and use the headset as a wearable projector to watch movies and TV shows.</p><p>Meta's entry-level VR headset is a modified version of the more powerful and expensive <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD1JTBSC?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" data-target="true" target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow">Quest 3</a>. Both models have 8GB RAM and use the Qualcomm Snapdragon XR2 chipset, which is a noticeable leap forward from the Quest 2. Outside of storage differences--the Quest 3 has 512GB--the internals are the same. Both versions come bundled with the wireless Touch Plus controllers, too. The Quest 3 has more advanced lenses, which results in a larger, clearer image. That said, the Quest 3S still looks great and can play the same games, and it even has slightly better battery life (2.5 hours).</p><p>With this deal, you're getting the Quest 3S 128GB model for half the price of the $499 Quest 3.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest 3S 256GB - Batman: Arkham Shadow Bundle</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0DDJZW3C9?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$329 (was $400)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>For $70 more you can double your storage to 256GB and get Batman: Arkham Shadow, a $50 game that's exclusive to the Quest 3 family. Arkham Shadow is an impressive action-adventure game that faithfully recreates the experience of being the Caped Crusader in VR. </p><p>New subscribers will also get a three-month free trial to Meta Horizon+. With Batman factored in, you're essentially getting seven free games over the next three months.</p></div>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest Elite Strap</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CD15C641?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$55 (was $70)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>You'll also want to pick up a few accessories for the Quest 3S if you decide to purchase it. The default strap on it is admittedly not the best, but you can easily fix that with the Quest Elite Strap. This has a better texture and design, and while it's normally $70, it's on sale for $55.</p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest Elite Strap with Battery</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B0CPYMDPB5?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$104 (was $130)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>The Elite Quest Strap with Battery is also a very good deal, as this equips the headset with some extra power. The battery is surprisingly lightweight for its design, and it sits at the rear of the headset to keep things balanced, adding around two more hours of playtime on a full charge. Normally $130, this is on sale for $104 during Prime Big Deal Days.</p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest Link Cable</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B081SHD773?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">$64 (was $80)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <p>You can also pick up the Meta Quest Link Cable and use it to connect your headset to your PC and its gaming library. While you can connect the Quest 3S to your PC wirelessly with the Air Link feature, the cable is nice to have as it make certain that there's less latency in your games.</p>                      </div>                                                                     <div>             <h2>                    <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Meta Quest 3S Carrying Cases</a>       </h2>                                   <h3>                      <a href="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20" rel="sponsored nofollow" target="_blank" data-event-tracking="{&quot;destUrl&quot;:&quot;https:\/\/www.amazon.com\/dp\/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20&quot;,&quot;dwLinkTag&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;,&quot;leadType&quot;:&quot;deal&quot;,&quot;linkLocation&quot;:&quot;BuyButton&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;seamlessScrollPage&quot;:&quot;1&quot;,&quot;searchDim&quot;:&quot;listicle|button&quot;}" data-track-page-event="{&quot;eventName&quot;:&quot;Monetization Link Clicked&quot;,&quot;merchantName&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;merchantPrice&quot;:&quot;&quot;}" data-vars-buy-link="https://www.amazon.com/dp/B09H68287R?tag=gamespot-primeday-20">Compact: $28.29 (was $50) | For Elite Strap: $54.29 (was $70)</a>         </h3>                                                                                                                      <div><p>Both of the official travel cases for the Quest 3S are on sale for Prime Big Deal Days. The larger case, shown above, is discounted to $54.29 (was $70) and is made for the headset with the Elite Strap (with or without Battery). If you don't buy the Elite Strap, go with the Compact Carrying Case, which is on sale for a much larger discount.</p><p>The Compact Carrying Case has a much larger discount, as it's nearly 50% off. If you buy the Elite Strap, you'll want the standard case. </p></div>                      </div>   </div><div data-embed-type="pinbox" data-ref-id="4304">  <ul>                              <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/nintendo-switch-2-powera-cheap-wireless-controller-super-mario-amazon-deals/1100-6535215/">Get Super Mario And Kirby Switch 2 Wireless Controllers For Up To 50% Off</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-audible-premium-plus-sign-up-prime-big-deal-days-black-friday-holiday-2025-deal/1100-6524536/">Audible Premium Plus Holiday Deal: Get 3 Audiobooks For $3</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/amazon-prime-big-deal-days-4k-blu-ray-best-deals/1100-6535093/">Prime Big Deal Days Movie Sale: Check Out Amazon's B2G1 Free 4K Blu-Ray Catalog</a></li>                          <li>         <span>+ Show More More Gaming, Tech, and Entertainment Deals &amp; Preorders Links (5)</span>       </li>          <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/rog-xbox-ally-preorder-guide/1100-6535007/">ROG Xbox Ally X Preorders In Stock At Best Buy, Sold Out Everywhere Else (September 27)</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/gallery/final-fantasy-magic-the-gathering-trading-cards-restock-where-to-buy-amazon-walmart-best-buy-target/2900-6271/">New Magic: The Gathering Final Fantasy Chocobo Bundle &amp; Scene Boxes Up For Preorder</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/lego-game-boy-restocked-at-amazon-and-its-shipping-early/1100-6533358/">You Can Get The $60 Lego Game Boy Early From Amazon</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/history-of-middle-earth-5440-page-box-set-drops-to-all-time-best-price-for-big-deal-days/1100-6526926/">Complete History Of Middle-Earth Collector's Box Set Restocked With $170 Discount</a></li>                         <li><a href="https://www.gamespot.com/articles/the-shining-movie-4k-blu-ray-special-edition-steelbook-the-film-vault/1100-6534223/">The Shining's New Numbered Limited Edition Is Up For Grabs At Amazon</a></li>   </ul> </div>
  
                        
    
        
        
  
